steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto Epar.Od. Livadochoriou-Karpasio/Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou
Continue to follow Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou

Posidonos turns left and becomes Ilia Iliou
Go through 2 roundabouts

Take the Ag. Efstratios - Limnos ferry
Toll road

Take the Ag. Efstratios - Lavrio ferry to Λαύριο
Toll road

Keep left to continue on Attiki Odos/A6, follow signs for Airport/Athina/E. Venizelos
Toll road
Take exit 8 to merge onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/A1/E75 toward PIREAS
At Πλ. Καραϊσκάκη, take the 1st exit onto Deligiorgi

Deligiorgi turns left and becomes Pireos/P. Tsaldari
Continue to follow Pireos
